{"tid":1644981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港人可以咁無情","createTime":"2019-10-10T17:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T17:40:59.000Z","uid":158148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"360846c7e7bb4edf5249e86b3326fa36f3d09153","tid":1644981,"uid":158148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"人地得15歲咋😭 邊有可能游泳叻走去跳海自殺架😭(仲要比人發現全裸！！！ 22號發現 10號你先黎同我判死因不明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我屌你老母死黑警 死全家 ！！！一條人命呀！！！<br />\n我真係唔明點解香港呢排頻繁發生呢d事情 <br />\n佢地都可以當無事發生 翻工放工<br />\n 唔阻我翻工就咩事都無 <br />\n你阻我翻工就屌你老母咁<br />\n萬一呢d事發生係你身邊既人身上呢？ 將心比心<br />\n我希望你地睇完會企出黎 睇下自己有咩可以幫到手<br />\n唔好再做只會翻工既香港人 <br />\nby 一個發緊夢既學生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNCTfb1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNCTfb1.png&h=23ad39bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3de8792e86d4a4a5988448ef92644635f2bf70f0","tid":1644981,"uid":305357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:31:32.000Z","msg":"大仔去科大啊<br />\n共產黨要入校董會啦<br />\n<br />\n讀緊科大嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644115</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n班大陸人靜靜雞係wechat吹哂雞去左投票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5792e3f8c60d6ecc989356f95e2dd1be139623","tid":1644981,"uid":158148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3de8792e86d4a4a5988448ef92644635f2bf70f0","tid":1644981,"uid":305357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:31:32.000Z","msg":"大仔去科大啊<br />\n共產黨要入校董會啦<br />\n<br />\n讀緊科大嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644115</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n班大陸人靜靜雞係wechat吹哂雞去左投票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:40:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己好撚無用<br />\n做唔到勇武<br />\n只係去做後勤 發夢"}]}